……」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 1"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[048]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「那是很久以前的事了。」"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【正宗】"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「可以的话就告诉我吧。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 8"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[049]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「只是无趣又常见的事喔。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 1"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[050]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「艾莲娜第一次使用魔法，"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["  是家里附近突然被恶魔攻击的时候。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 10"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[051]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「父母在我面前被攻击，"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["  我吓得动弹不得。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 1"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[052]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「或许是因为恶魔寻求魔力而攻击大人，"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["  所以艾莲娜没事。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 8"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[053]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「但是父母在我面前，倒在地上一动也不动。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 8"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[054]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「就算出声求救，但是大家都在拼命逃离恶魔，"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["  完全没人来帮忙，我还以为已经不行了。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 1"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[055]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「这时候，我的身体擅自行动了起来。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 2"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[056]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「回过神来，父母的伤已经治好了。」"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【正宗】"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「治愈魔法吗？」"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[057]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「嗯。艾莲娜最擅长的魔法。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 1"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[058]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「后来赶到的勇者打败了恶魔，平息了骚动。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 10"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[059]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「然后镇上的修女就开始调查骚动的原因。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 8"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[060]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「原来恶魔是居民召唤的。」"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【正宗】"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「什么……」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 1"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\>【艾莲娜】\\m[19]\\z[061]"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["「好像是恶魔信徒的样子。"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["  虽然不知道为什么要召唤恶魔，"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["  但是那个人当然被抓起来判了无期徒刑。」"]},{"code":356,"indent":0,"parameters":["スキット 表情 エレナ f 10"]},{"cod